    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入勇敢者的行列</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在白雪皑皑的山峰脚下，有一座陷入沉眠的古老国度。财富传说与超乎想象的奇迹吸引了许多人前去叩响王国的大门，但回来的人却寥寥无几。玩家将扮演马尔科，一个茁壮成长的英雄，证实自身价值，并讨伐妄图吞噬大地的恶魔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/3fdfcc63b5530eff6df31c97eb30aa8e.poster.avif?t=1729771585\" width=560 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/3fdfcc63b5530eff6df31c97eb30aa8e.webm?t=1729771585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/3fdfcc63b5530eff6df31c97eb30aa8e.mp4?t=1729771585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传统2D艺术：细致描摹出栩栩如生的扎古拉大陆，全程手工的画面绘制及动画创作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 充满挑战，但彰显公平的游戏玩法：精确灵敏的控制。跳跃，战斗，并突破挑战。与强大的敌人战斗，并屠戮古老的恶魔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索扎古拉的广袤土地：一个拥有数百房间的巨大非线性地图。解决谜题，寻找隐藏宝藏，将一切游戏元素融入以斯拉夫文化为灵感创作的童话背景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 与神秘角色相逢：使用传统2D逐帧动画，生动刻画大量可爱伙伴与恐怖敌人的形象。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 掌握新能力：发现新技能，来让你与最凶残的敌人正面交锋。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 揭晓所有秘密：深入世界内部，发掘隐藏区域和难以言喻的宝藏。收集所有碎片，拼凑出古老的谜团。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/c8b8b30aeef3ab99a6c489008d874003.avif?t=1729771585\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/f006aa186ab85ab14ebc5615766926ee.poster.avif?t=1729771585\" width=562 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/f006aa186ab85ab14ebc5615766926ee.webm?t=1729771585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/f006aa186ab85ab14ebc5615766926ee.mp4?t=1729771585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>探索失落王国的秘密</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/90a319752e4165b81441d1a2269645c3.poster.avif?t=1729771585\" width=560 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/90a319752e4165b81441d1a2269645c3.webm?t=1729771585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186470/extras/90a319752e4165b81441d1a2269645c3.mp4?t=1729771585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>结交在旅程中助你一臂之力的盟友</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"src=&quot;{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Vlashko_boss_f.gif/img\\\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span><br>,击溃敌手，绝境逢生<br>,<br>,<br>&quot;]</p>",
